sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    %% Flow 1: Client Request Through Gateway Ingress Stack
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,Backend: Flow 1: Client Request Through Gateway Ingress Stack

        participant Client as Client Browser
        participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
        participant Envoy as Gateway Service<br/>(Envoy Proxy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant AuthProxy as kube-auth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS (service CA)
        participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth /<br/>OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant Backend as Backend Application<br/>(HTTPRoute target)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

        Client->>Route: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+
        Route->>Envoy: HTTPS/443<br/>re-encrypt TLS
        Envoy->>AuthProxy: ext_authz check<br/>HTTPS/8443 (service CA)<br/>Cookie or Bearer token
        AuthProxy->>OAuth: Validate credentials<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>OAuthClient / OIDC creds
        OAuth-->>AuthProxy: Auth response
        AuthProxy-->>Envoy: Auth decision
        Envoy->>Backend: Lua filter forwards<br/>HTTP/8080 (cluster-internal)<br/>Bearer token (forwarded)
        Backend-->>Envoy: Response
        Envoy-->>Route: Response
        Route-->>Client: HTTPS Response
    end

    %% Flow 2: Component Deployment Lifecycle
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 2: Component Deployment Lifecycle

        participant User as User / OLM
        participant DSCCR as DataScienceCluster CR
        participant DSCCtrl as DSC Controller
        participant Registry as Component Registry<br/>(in-process)
        participant CompHandler as Component Handler
        participant CompCR as Component CR<br/>(e.g., Dashboard)
        participant CompCtrl as Component Controller
        participant Kustomize as Kustomize Renderer<br/>(in-process)
        participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS

        User->>DSCCR: Create/Update DSC<br/>K8s API HTTPS
        DSCCR->>DSCCtrl: Watch event
        DSCCtrl->>Registry: Iterate components
        Registry->>CompHandler: Init component
        CompHandler->>CompCR: Create Component CR<br/>K8s API HTTPS
        CompCR->>CompCtrl: Watch event
        CompCtrl->>Kustomize: Render manifests
        Kustomize-->>CompCtrl: Rendered resources
        CompCtrl->>K8sAPI: Server-Side Apply<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>CompCtrl: Applied
        CompCtrl-->>DSCCtrl: Status update
    end

    %% Flow 3: Monitoring Data Collection
    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over AppPod,Thanos: Flow 3: Monitoring Data Collection

        participant AppPod as Application Pods
        participant OTelCol as OpenTelemetry Collector<br/>4317/TCP gRPC
        participant Tempo as Tempo<br/>4317/TCP gRPC
        participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>(MonitoringStack)<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
        participant SvcMonitor as Component<br/>ServiceMonitors
        participant Thanos as Thanos Querier<br/>10902/TCP HTTP

        AppPod->>OTelCol: Traces<br/>gRPC/4317<br/>Conditional TLS<br/>Bearer token
        OTelCol->>Tempo: Store traces<br/>gRPC/4317<br/>Conditional TLS<br/>Multitenancy token
        Prometheus->>SvcMonitor: Scrape metrics<br/>HTTPS/8443 TLS<br/>ServiceAccount
        Thanos->>Prometheus: Query metrics<br/>HTTP/10902
    end
